'''ASUS ROG Army''' was a professional esports club founded in January 2016.

== History ==
'''ASUS ROG Army''' wants to mark a before and after in esports in Spain. It is the big bet of ASUS Republic of Gamers by putting a Spanish club at the same level of professionalism that the first international club. 

